  ### When to Use Each Approach

  | Approach | Use Case |
  |----------|----------|
  | **Event-based** (`event_id`) | Tie conversion to specific action (checkout button click, form submit) |
  | **Visitor-based** (`visitor_id`) | Direct conversions, offline imports, webhook integrations |

